AHRS - Class in com.kauailabs.navx.ftc
The AHRS class provides an interface to AHRS capabilities of the KauaiLabs navX Robotics Navigation Sensor via I2C on the Android- based FTC robotics control system, where communications occur via the "Core Device Interface Module" produced by Modern Robotics, inc.
